{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1a1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's you, Ayesha.<CR>Welcome."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "(I'm scared to ask, but there's something I need to check with him.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Umm, Mix Master, what happened to the Red Devil food from last time...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that...?<CR>Well, there was a fierce result."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I'm scared to ask, but what happened...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "First, I called him over, telling<CR>him I'd treat him to a meal, but I<CR>think he suspected something was up…"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I had never treated him to a meal before, so that was a mistake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xab,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I successfully got him to eat the Red Devil food, and it put him through one hell of an experience, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "That guy spiked my drink with alcohol!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Ohh, so you were both thinking on the same level."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "No, I was one step above him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "\"Juris, let's just call it a tie for today. Now, drink this water to rinse your mouth out.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x182,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's what I said as I offered him some water."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oh...but drinking water after eating something spicy just accentuates the spiciness even more..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "You see? I'm quite the schemer, aren't I? So I sealed my victory and took a sip of water..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But that guy had spiked it with alcohol again! What a jerk!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm sure the blame falls on both sides..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Well, so the result ended up being a fierce tie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "We were both knocked out the next day, unable to do anything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x112,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "It was a battle where we lost many<CR>things...and gained nothing. However!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I now feel a sense of accomplishment in my heart. I did it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I-I don't know if I'd agree with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Well, we called a truce for a while. If we kept going like that, our bodies wouldn't last."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "You should just end it instead of calling a truce. I really think you should stop..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That's an impossible request.<CR>This is our way of life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'll keep it a secret that you gave me the recipe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "So don't worry about that.<CR>Hahaha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "(I don't think that's the problem.<CR>I wonder if this really turned out<CR>okay...)"
        }
    ]
}